
"We can always attack or chase you out," tortoiseshell tom stated.
"You can try," Tawny added. "I've been a rogue for a very long time, I know my ways of escaping."
Darksky licked his lips nervously. "Fine! We'll guide you, but I'll be watching you," he growled as he narrowed his eyes.
Tawny shrugged. "Whatever you want."
"So it's settled. Once you studied your former home, you may leave," Cherryshine said, as she finally remembered who the she-cat was. From the looks of it, she was trusted enough in this territory because "Tawny" had no grudge on RiverClan. She may even be useful against the other clans.